yingyinNormal.en: Well, of course, that's entirely up to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当然，这取决于你。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, he just told me that he's not entirely happy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是他刚说他也不开心。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you saying that you're not entirely happy about this?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你的意思是你也不想走？

yingyinNormal.en: So I'm just gonna leave it entirely up to the gods of fate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我决定交给命运之神。

yingyinNormal.en: You don't really want that, do you? No, it's not entirely true.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你实际上不是这样想的，是不是？不全是这样的。

yingyinNormal.en: I hadn't been entirely truthful with you, Jane. About what, sir?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有完全对你说实话，简。关于什么？

yingyinNormal.en: But none of this has to do with me. No, this is entirely about you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是这都跟我没有关系，仅跟你自己有关。

yingyinNormal.en: The embarrassment will be entirely my own. This is on my shoulders.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那也是丢我的脸。这事儿我来担。

yingyinNormal.en: Why is he bothering you with it? I'm not entirely sure. What's that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他为什么来找您？我也不太确定，那是什么？

yingyinNormal.en: We are two days out. On the dais. You are going about this entirely wrong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 两天后就开始了。贵宾席。你的算盘完全打错了。

yingyinNormal.en: It's apple pecan. I haven't been entirely honest with you love. I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 苹果核桃馅的。我没有完全跟你坦白，对不起。

yingyinNormal.en: Our interest in this place is entirely in the intellectual property. The code.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们对这个地方唯一的兴趣就是知识产权，就是代码。

yingyinNormal.en: It's called "Marble with Wood," and let's just say it's made entirely of marble.
yingyinNormal.zh: 雕塑名叫《大理石和"硬木"》，这么说吧，雕塑完全是大理石做的。

yingyinNormal.en: You're boring people, "sweetie". Although, sometimes, she omits the veil entirely.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别这么无聊，“甜心”。但有时她就是赤裸裸的讽刺。

yingyinNormal.en: 17 years and still evolving with the times remains an entirely foreign concept to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 十七年都过去了，你仍然不打算与时代同步。

yingyinNormal.en: Every movement I made was entirely random, every new personality just on the roll of a dice!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的每一步都是完全随机的，每个新身份都全凭掷骰子决定！

yingyinNormal.en: We've been studying Formic flight patterns for three months now, but they seem entirely random.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三个月来我们一直在研习，虫族战机的作战规律，但看起来全无规律可言。

yingyinNormal.en: Russo was in the passenger seat when he died. That's not entirely accurate. I saw the police report.
yingyinNormal.zh: Russo死的时候在副驾驶座上。这话不完全准确。我看过警方报告。

yingyinNormal.en: Many Americans do not realize that the war in North Korea was entirely the fault of the United States.
yingyinNormal.zh: 许多美国人并没有明白，发生在朝鲜的战争完全是美国的错。

yingyinNormal.en: The further out you venture, the more intense the experience gets. How far you want to go is entirely up to you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 随着进一步的冒险，你会得到更刺激的体验，进行到何种地步都由你决定。
